Test-case wm/move_edge_resistance
<ol>
<li title="action">Open an application</li>
<li title="action">Drag the title bar slowly to the left or right of the screen until the window edge gets out of the screen</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">Window resists a bit before getting out of the screen</li>
</ol>
</ol>
Test-case wm/active
<ol>
<li title="action">Start two applications</li>
<li title="action">Click on the window for the inactive application</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">Window gets the focus and is shown above the other application window.</li>
<li title="expected_result">Window title bar lights up (lighter title, colored buttons).</li>
<li title="expected_result">Previous active window title bar darkens (dark title, monochrome buttons).</li>
</ol>
</ol>
