Test-case wm/stacking
<ol>
<li title="action">open an application and make it maximised</li>
<li title="action">Attempt to open the dash</li>
<li title="action">Attempt to open indicators</li>
<ol>
<li title="expected_result">The dash and all indicators appear stacked correctly on top of the window</li>
</ol>
</ol>
